---
title: Paneer & Lemon Pepper Roast Veggie Bowl with Almonds & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful paneer meets roasted vegetables tossed with lemon pepper spices, and there’s a tangy yoghurt dressing plus toasted almonds to finish it off.

*Unfortunately, this week's courgette was in short supply, so we've replaced it with parsnip. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
